fields.title: Specialties
fields.body_text:
From inception through to completion, Project X:ion provides an extensive range of services for the international property and construction industry.

 

COST MANAGEMENT

  • Accurate estimating capabilities

  • Realistic budgets are stringently adhered to, from concept drawings to tender processes and construction

  

PROJECT MANAGEMENT

  • The key phases of a project — initiation and concept, planning and development; construction and execution, handover and evaluation

  • Establish project objectives, undertake an appraisal of the project and document the process in the project plan

  

DEVELOPMENT MANAGEMENT

  • Strategic property development and property investment analysis

  • Prepare independent feasibilities and analysis based on development and specific property sectors

  • Manage development processes through local councils and statutory bodies

 

TURN-KEY PROJECTS

  • One-stop solution for property and construction

  • One point of contact to ensure fluid communication

fields.title: About Us
fields.body_text:
Project X: ion is a diverse, multi-disciplined property and construction consultancy. We are current with the systems and regulations pertaining to property and construction, applying our knowledge in tandem with the cultures and processes of countries in and around Asia.

 

We understand that a project is about maintaining a synergy between all components. Our services go through a single point of contact ensuring consistency throughout your experience with Project X:ion.

 

Keeping abreast of the latest technology advancements, we constantly integrate innovative techniques into our stable of services for a synergistic result. 

 

Sector Knowledge
  • Aged Care
  • Leisure / Recreation
  • Commercial
  • Public and Government
  • Education
  • Residential
  • Hotels & Resorts
  • Retail
  • Industrial / Warehouses
  • Transport
  • Infrastructure
